Package: sofa
Title: R Connector to CouchDB
Description: Provides an interface to the NoSQL database CouchDB
    (<http://couchdb.apache.org>).  Methods are provided for managing
    databases within CouchDB, including creating/deleting/updating/transferring,
    and managing documents within databases. In addition, we facilitate
    connecting with remote CouchDB databases including Iriscouch
    (<http://www.iriscouch.com>) and Cloudant (<https://cloudant.com>).
    Documents can be inserted directly from vectors, lists,
    data.frames, and JSON.
Version: 0.1.9.9100
